{
  "prompt": "A cross-sectional technical illustration of an integrated bicycle hub motor and internal gear hub (IGH) system. The left side of the unit shows a BLDC hub motor with a planetary gear reduction system. The right side shows a 3-speed internal gear hub system (similar to Shimano Nexus) with sun gear, planet gears, and ring gear. The motor stator is fixed to the axle, while the rotor spins with the hub shell. Bearings support both sides of the axle. The outer shell includes spoke flanges and disc brake mount. Hollow axle allows internal wiring. Detailed technical, cutaway style with labels and metallic textures.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "An isometric cutaway (exploded view) technical illustration of an integrated electric bicycle hub motor and internal gear hub (IGH) system. The left section features a BLDC hub motor with a planetary gear reducer, showing the rotor, stator, and gear teeth. The right section features a 3-speed internal gear hub, with visible sun gear, planet gears, ring gear, and shifting mechanism. Axle passes through the center with bearings and internal wiring channel. The outer aluminum shell includes spoke flanges and disc brake mount. Highly detailed, metallic textures, labeled components, and realistic technical rendering.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}
